sentence: Among the underlying components of the S&P 500 index, we saw noteworthy options trading volume today in Blackrock Inc (Symbol: BLK), where a total of 3,070 contracts have traded so far, representing approximately 307,000 underlying shares.
That amounts to about 48.1% of BLK's average daily trading volume over the past month of 637,740 shares.
Especially high volume was seen for the $430 strike put option expiring October 18, 2019, with 178 contracts trading so far today, representing approximately 17,800 underlying shares of BLK.
